María Martín https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mar%C3%ADa_Mart%C3%ADn 0 María Martín (born 14 July 1923) is a retired Spanish actress. After making her screen debut in 1943 Martín appeared in around eighty films during her career including Dawn of America (1951) and Bilbao (1978) María_Martín ( born 14_July_1923 ) is a_retired_Spanish_actress .
